---
title: Middle Eastern Pork & Currant Filo Cigars with Garden Salad & Tahini Yoghurt
description: These savoury cigars are the ultimate finger food! Layers of flaky filo encase a delicious spiced pork mince filling with pops of sweetness from currants and onion. Paired with a refreshing salad and tangy tahini yoghurt, this dish is perfectly balanced and sure to satisfy.
